      <title>泽连斯基呼吁亚洲领导人参加峰会以结束俄罗斯战争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-02/zelenskiy-asks-asia-leaders-to-join-summit-to-end-russia-s-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统泽连斯基呼吁亚洲领导人参加本月的峰会，讨论乌克兰的和平蓝图。泽连斯基认为，开辟一条结束俄罗斯战争的道路将有助于缓解全球不稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-02/zelenskiy-asks-asia-leaders-to-join-summit-to-end-russia-s-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 05:33:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普加入他曾试图禁止的中国应用 TikTok：Politico</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-02/trump-joins-tiktok-a-chinese-app-he-tried-to-ban-politico</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据 Politico 报道，前总统唐纳德·特朗普已加入 TikTok，拥抱这款他曾试图在美国禁止的中国应用程序。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-02/trump-joins-tiktok-a-chinese-app-he-tried-to-ban-politico</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 04:55:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
