      <title>朝鲜向韩国投放数百只装满碎石的气球</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-02/north-korea-sends-hundreds-of-rubble-filled-balloons-to-south</link>
      <description><![CDATA[首尔官员称，过去一周，朝鲜向边境放飞了数百只装满碎石的气球，以报复上个月韩国活动分子向朝鲜散发反平壤传单。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-02/north-korea-sends-hundreds-of-rubble-filled-balloons-to-south</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 04:08:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>无论谁获胜，英国债务问题都将牵动下届政府的命运</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-02/uk-debt-hangover-ties-next-government-s-hands-whoever-wins</link>
      <description><![CDATA[无论哪个政党在7月4日赢得英国大选，巨大的债务危机都将接踵而至，这将严重限制在民意调查中领先的工党或执政的保守党在执政期间的行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-02/uk-debt-hangover-ties-next-government-s-hands-whoever-wins</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日韩将加强防务关系，结束五年僵局</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-02/japan-south-korea-to-boost-defense-ties-end-5-year-stand-off</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本和韩国国防部长周六晚间表示，在就防止海上争端再次发生的措施达成协议后，两国将恢复高层军事会谈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-02/japan-south-korea-to-boost-defense-ties-end-5-year-stand-off</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 03:03:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
